<HL>
   Hasbro's Net Jumped
   61% in Fourth Period
   As Revenue Rose 54%
</HL>
<DATE>
02/11/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C18
</SO>
<CO>
   HAS
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
ENTERTAINMENT AND LEISURE (ENT)
EARNINGS (ERN)
RECREATION, ENTERTAINMENT, TOYS, MOVIES, PHOTOGRAPHY (REC)
TOY MANUFACTURERS (TMF)
</IN>
<NS>
